Package: semScreenR
Type: Package
Title: Deterministic Screening and Validation for SEM
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Mohamed Ali", family = "S", role = c("aut","cre"), email = "you@example.com"))
Description: Rule-based, cross-validated screening workflow for Structural Equation
    Modeling (SEM). Provides audit trails, caps on row/item removal, careless
    responding detection, and APA-style reporting.
